    },
    {
      "id": "ag-note-legend",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 3016,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 110,
      "meta": {
        "origin": "agent"
      },
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Legend** — edge color/line/head is driven by edgeType: cyan solid arrow = data-flow · amber solid open-arrow = request · amber dotted open-arrow = response · violet solid diamond = event · grey dashed arrow = dependency · grey dotted circle = reference."
    },
    {
      "id": "ag-note-escalation",
      "x": 728,
      "y": 3016,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 140,
      "meta": {
        "origin": "agent"
      },
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Escalation & 24h window** — a free-form reply is only allowed within 24h of the customer's last inbound; outside that window (or for an owner notification) msgflow sends a pre-approved WhatsApp utility template instead. Escalation pauses auto-replies for that conversation until the owner resolves it."
    },
    {
      "id": "ag-note-secrets",
      "x": 1236,
      "y": 3016,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 120,
      "meta": {
        "origin": "agent"
      },
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Secret encryption** — zavu API keys and Google refresh tokens are AES-256-GCM envelope-encrypted in `core.crypto`; the key-encryption-key lives only in the environment/secret manager. `secret_key_version` enables rotation without a data migration."
    },
    {
      "id": "ag-note-tenancy",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 3244,
      "width": 860,
      "height": 90,
      "meta": {
        "origin": "agent"
      },
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Multi-tenancy guard** — every table carries `business_id`; every query is `WHERE business_id = :bid`-scoped. `business_id` is injected into agent tools via closure/RunnableConfig — never an LLM-supplied argument — so the agent cannot read across tenants."
    }
  ],
